---
title: Herb Crusted Bison Burger with Chunky Steak Fries
description: It's time to celebrate Canadian-raised bison - packed full of flavour and extra lean for delicious burgers. The rosemary and thyme crust boosts the earthy goodness, while creamy gooey cheddar cascades down the patty. And you can't have a burger without chunky steak cut fries!
